details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Finally, I have almost caught up with my target.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: The armored corps is here, but those wimpy infantry units didn't manage to keep the pace.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: This might prove to be an issue, so deep behind enemy lines, they actually do have quite a lot of troops and buildings.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: It seems that a lot of Jade Twilight forces are standing down. They do have radar towers, though. I'm sure, that as soon as me, or any of my units, get's too close, they will sound an alarm.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Even if I would manage to push through all these defensive lines with my armoured force, I wouldn't be able to hold these positions.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Luckily, I don't have to. All I need to do is to use my awesome Commando abilities, get close to the Prince, and get him out.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Some of the foliage in this area is very dense. I should be able to use it to my advantage. Tall grass will protect me from being detected, as long as the alarm hasn't been activated.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: A Rocket Artillery found some old, forgotten route through the wilderness. Normally, it wouldn't do me much good, but thanks to their long range, they can assist from afar.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: In the meantime, Jade Twilight might send some units to my encampment. I have to defend it, as it is my only way out.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Tybalt is not going to slip away this time!
Infiltrate Jade Twilight base.
Defend Sapphire Dawn camp.
Commando Blake must survive.
(Optional) Do not raise an alarm.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: Alarm! Enemy infiltration detected!
(Failed) Do not raise an alarm.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: No! With that route closed, there is no way for me to get Prince Tybalt out of here! This operation is a bust.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: I wasn't... fast... enough...

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Almost there. All I have to do is to approach the target and grab him!
Capture Prince Tybalt.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: There is a guard ahead. They will spot me if I just try to sneak around the tree line

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: I have to take them out somehow. Or I could just wait a bit and use my skill to get across those trees undetected.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Treeline is thinner here. I should be able to get through it using my Infiltration skill.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: I'm pretty sure they will still spot me though. Enemy units might go after me into the tall grass to investigate, but should not raise an alarm just yet. In that case I should just keep going.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: I've got you now!
Ah, Blake. Hot-headed as always.

details.name: Captain Claude
details.text: Surrender, you have nowhere to run now.

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: I warned you, that next time we meet it would be different. I won't run away anymore.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Oh you... !!!

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: He slipped away!

details.name: Captain Claude
details.text: Blake is a master infiltrator. We probably wouldn't be able to catch him anyway. Just let him run, he won't be able to pester you anymore.

details.name: Captain Claude
details.text: Our transport to the Jade Oasis is waiting. Let's go.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Another guard, this time on patrol. They could be taken out, or I could just wait for them to get around the corner and run.
